<i>noun</i>: 속병 [속ː뼝], 상심 [상심], 비통 [비ː통] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>속병 [속ː뼝]</dt><br>
<dd>1. internal disease</dd><br>
<dd>몸속의 생기는 병.</dd><br>
<dd>A disease occurring inside a body.</dd><br>
<dd>2. intestinal disease</dd><br>
<dd>위나 장에 생기는 병.</dd><br>
<dd>A disease occurring in stomach or intestine.</dd><br>
<dd>3. heartache; heartbreak</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 몹시 아픈 것.</dd><br>
<dd>Mental suffering.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>상심 [상심]</dt><br>
<dd>heartbreak; grief</dd><br>
<dd>슬픔이나 걱정 등으로 마음 아파함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being mentally painful due to sorrow, worry, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>비통 [비ː통]</dt><br>
<dd>grief; heartbreak</dd><br>
<dd>매우 슬퍼서 마음이 아픔.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of feeling deeply sad and heartbroken.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>